{"tid":1440424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九月罷課大行動出現鳥 學生自決","createTime":"2019-08-10T12:13:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T19:36:35.000Z","uid":61876,"like":125,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f3f7e37c4d0bf65340d22625bef2a07ef85d40bb","tid":1440424,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:13:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/10/200458_0fad5cb795e14f9f4315883b4956f45b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F10%2F200458_0fad5cb795e14f9f4315883b4956f45b.png&h=e0d0d125&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日收到風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暑假到而家已經過咗一半啦 剩返嘅日子只係得一個月都冇<br />\n咁喺開學之後有咩做可以維持返中學生對運動嘅參與呢？<br />\n費事一開學就冇咁多人留意場運動呢？<br />\nExact7ly罷課啦梗係 <br />\n不過考慮到可能唔同學生對罷課集會可能有唔同嘅意見<br />\n於是乎就有問卷收集大家關於罷課集會嘅意見<br />\n<a href=\"http://tiny.cc/SSStrikeQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftiny.cc%2FSSStrikeQ&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPKhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=ed3f2b33\" target=\"_blank\">tiny.cc/SSStrikeQ</a><br />\n8月14星期三就問卷截止 大家快啲去填下"},{"pid":"b2b87f9cad8ecf4d703462cf80d17bbcbb991749","tid":1440424,"uid":61876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f3f7e37c4d0bf65340d22625bef2a07ef85d40bb","tid":1440424,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:13:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/10/200458_0fad5cb795e14f9f4315883b4956f45b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F10%2F200458_0fad5cb795e14f9f4315883b4956f45b.png&h=e0d0d125&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日收到風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暑假到而家已經過咗一半啦 剩返嘅日子只係得一個月都冇<br />\n咁喺開學之後有咩做可以維持返中學生對運動嘅參與呢？<br />\n費事一開學就冇咁多人留意場運動呢？<br />\nExact7ly罷課啦梗係 <br />\n不過考慮到可能唔同學生對罷課集會可能有唔同嘅意見<br />\n於是乎就有問卷收集大家關於罷課集會嘅意見<br />\n<a href=\"http://tiny.cc/SSStrikeQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftiny.cc%2FSSStrikeQ&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPKhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=ed3f2b33\" target=\"_blank\">tiny.cc/SSStrikeQ</a><br />\n8月14星期三就問卷截止 大家快啲去填下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:13:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://tiny.cc/SSStrikeQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftiny.cc%2FSSStrikeQ&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPKhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=ed3f2b33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tiny.cc/SSStrikeQ</a>"},{"pid":"2e4cbcd9653d7f56a6177fe03c2e503a0ba69ae1","tid":1440424,"uid":61876,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:16:39.000Z","msg":"大家入去做問卷啊!<br />\n九月罷課真係好重要 可能係運動轉捩點!<br />\n始終學生開學就少咗好多時間參與運動 而罷課只要做得好<br />\n就可以開個頭比班學生喺學期內繼續參與運動！<br />\n唔單止可以攞到attention 亦都可以延續學生對運動嘅熱情!"},{"pid":"b6948e4d6d01e50936eb27fd6460b2b863063006","tid":1440424,"uid":126276,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:19:14.000Z","msg":"我都覺得罷課要搞㗎喇 不過等咗好耐都冇人搞 最緊要可以畀班和理非學生返學嗰陣接力 唔好畀政府拖到九月收我哋皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBTW 呢個係咪姐係香港眾志今日喺ig擺嗰個 我見張圖好似一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e67f95387de653a66de676b8ff30006003573908","tid":1440424,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6948e4d6d01e50936eb27fd6460b2b863063006","tid":1440424,"uid":126276,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:19:14.000Z","msg":"我都覺得罷課要搞㗎喇 不過等咗好耐都冇人搞 最緊要可以畀班和理非學生返學嗰陣接力 唔好畀政府拖到九月收我哋皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBTW 呢個係咪姐係香港眾志今日喺ig擺嗰個 我見張圖好似一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/no